---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="UNMASK Blueprint Series — Books & Manuals"
  description="The UNMASK Blueprint Series by Nikki Cates. Practitioner-developed diagnostic workbooks for organizations and leaders ready to dismantle structural burnout at the root."
  section="st"
  accentColor="teal"
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-st-gradient"></div>
    <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-[3px] bg-teal-DEFAULT"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 70% 40%, rgba(13,148,136,0.09) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>
    <div class="container-mid relative z-10">
      <span class="st-tag mb-5 inline-flex animate-on-scroll">Publications</span>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-6xl text-light font-bold mb-5 animate-on-scroll">
        UNMASK Blueprint<br/>
        <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT">Series.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mb-3 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
        These are not self-help books.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted text-base max-w-2xl mb-10 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.15s">
        The UNMASK Blueprint Series is a practitioner-developed diagnostic framework in written form —
        built for leaders, consultants, HR professionals, and organizational architects who are
        done treating the symptoms of structural burnout and ready to examine the design.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── BOOKS ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

        <!-- Vol 1 -->
        <div class="card teal-hover flex flex-col gap-5 animate-on-scroll">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <!-- Book cover placeholder -->
            <div class="w-28 h-36 rounded-md shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/40"
                 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f4c7a 0%, #0d9488 100%);">
              <div class="p-3">
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-tight">UNMASK</p>
                <p class="font-body text-white/70 text-xs">Vol. 1</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="st-tag text-xs mb-2 inline-flex">Vol. 1</span>
              <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-light font-bold mb-2">
                UNMASK Blueprint
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">by Nikki Cates</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Volume 1 introduces the UNMASK Framework in its full conceptual and practical scope.
            It is the entry point into structural burnout diagnosis — walking leaders through each
            pillar of the framework with reflective exercises, diagnostic questions, and organizational
            application guidance.
          </p>

          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-xs font-700 uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">This volume is for:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {[
                'Leaders seeking to understand structural burnout at a foundational level',
                'Consultants building a structural diagnostic practice',
                'HR professionals looking for a framework beyond engagement surveys',
                'Executive coaches and organizational development practitioners',
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-muted">
                  <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0">→</span>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
            <a
              href="https://strategicunmasking.com/unmask-vol-1"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="btn-teal !text-sm"
            >
              Get Vol. 1 →
            </a>
            <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal !text-sm">
              Ask About Bulk / Institutional
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Vol 2 -->
        <div class="card teal-hover flex flex-col gap-5 animate-on-scroll" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-5">
            <div class="w-28 h-36 rounded-md shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center border border-teal-DEFAULT/40"
                 style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0a3356 0%, #0f4c7a 50%, #0d9488 100%);">
              <div class="p-3">
                <p class="font-heading text-white text-xs font-bold leading-tight">UNMASK</p>
                <p class="font-body text-white/70 text-xs">Vol. 2</p>
                <p class="font-body text-teal-light text-xs mt-1">Institutional</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="st-tag text-xs mb-2 inline-flex">Vol. 2 · Institutional Manual</span>
              <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-light font-bold mb-2">
                UNMASK Blueprint Master Manual
              </h2>
              <p class="text-muted text-sm">by Nikki Cates</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Volume 2 is the institutional-grade deployment manual. Built for organizations, licensed
            practitioners, and leadership teams implementing the UNMASK Framework at scale.
            It includes the full diagnostic engine across all six pillars, scoring matrices,
            team facilitation guides, and recalibration planning templates.
          </p>

          <div>
            <p class="font-body text-xs font-700 uppercase tracking-widest text-muted mb-3">Includes:</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {[
                'Full 6-pillar diagnostic across LMI, RAA, and ITC indices',
                'Team facilitation protocols for group implementation',
                'ROI framework for organizational investment justification',
                'Recalibration planning templates',
                'Licensing terms for practitioner and institutional use',
              ].map((item) => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-muted">
                  <span class="text-teal-DEFAULT shrink-0">→</span>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-auto">
            <a
              href="https://strategicunmasking.com/unmask-vol-2"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener"
              class="btn-teal !text-sm"
            >
              Get Vol. 2 →
            </a>
            <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal !text-sm">
              Institutional License Inquiry
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── INTERACTIVE WEB APP ────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad bg-[#0c1525]">
    <div class="container-mid">
      <div class="card border-teal-DEFAULT/30 bg-teal-glow p-10 text-center animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Digital Tool</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl text-light mb-4">
          UNMASK Vol. 2 Interactive Web Application
        </h2>
        <p class="text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          The UNMASK Manual is also available as a fully interactive web application — featuring
          a live diagnostic router, ROI Engine with adjustable sliders, and six-pillar visualization
          dashboard. Built for teams and institutions implementing the framework digitally.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://nikkicates.github.io/unmask-manual/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="btn-teal"
        >
          Access the Web Application →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <!-- ─── LICENSING ─────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="section-pad">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <span class="st-tag mb-4 inline-flex">Licensing</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl text-light">Use UNMASK in Your Organization</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {[
          {
            icon: '👤',
            name: 'Individual License',
            desc: 'Personal use for leaders, coaches, and individual practitioners. Single-user access to both volumes.',
            cta: 'Purchase Individual',
          },
          {
            icon: '👥',
            name: 'Team License',
            desc: 'For organizational teams (up to 25 people). Includes facilitation guides and team-implementation protocols.',
            cta: 'Inquire About Team',
          },
          {
            icon: '🏢',
            name: 'Institutional License',
            desc: 'Enterprise-wide or multi-team deployment. Practitioner certification pathway included. Custom scope.',
            cta: 'Request Institutional Briefing',
          },
        ].map((lic) => (
          <div class="card teal-hover text-center flex flex-col gap-4 animate-on-scroll">
            <span class="text-3xl mx-auto">{lic.icon}</span>
            <p class="font-heading text-light font-semibold">{lic.name}</p>
            <p class="text-muted text-sm flex-1">{lic.desc}</p>
            <a href="/structural-burnout/briefing" class="btn-outline-teal !text-sm justify-center">
              {lic.cta}
            </a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
